title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1989-12-28
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll
Feel Like A Stranger
Dire Wolf
Little Red Rooster
Ramble On Rose
Queen Jane Approximately
Just A Little Light
Let It Grow

Set 2

Foolish Heart >
Looks Like Rain >
Eyes Of The World >
Drums >
Space >
Gimme Some Lovin' >
All Along The Watchtower >
Stella Blue >
Turn On Your Lovelight

Encore:
U.S. Blues

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
